domain.action.contracts

Interface IActionRequest

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ActionRequest, CatchActionRequest, MoveActionRequest

    public interface IActionRequest
    A request for IAction. It contains a list of Location indices and a method to differentiate between move and catch requests.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Location getEnd()
      Returns the Location corresponding to the last index.
      java.util.List<Location> getLocations()
      Returns the List of indices in this IActionRequest.
      int getNumberOfCatches()
      Returns the number of catches.
      Player getPlayer()
      Returns the Player that requested this ActionRequest.
      Location getStart()
      Returns the Location corresponding to the first index.
      boolean isCatch()
      Returns true if this IAction performs a catch, false otherwise.
